title: #40 -  Zedd Reveals His Valorant Addiction & Why Streaming is Harder Than Music
itunes:title: #40 -  Zedd Reveals His Valorant Addiction & Why Streaming is Harder Than Music
description: On this in-studio episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast presented by Cash App, Grammy Award-winning DJ & producer Zedd comes onto the show to talk about his outlook on the future of Valorant, how he did 3 concerts in LA & China in 24 hours, his 200+ sneaker collection, working with Skrillex, and more!
